I agree.

33
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,910
Agree.

34
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,470
I... I also agree.

35
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,470
- Mrs. Qian.
- Han.

36
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:25,310
Mrs. Liu.

37
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,000
Han, why are you here?

38
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,190
It's raining outside.

39
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,280
I got you an umbrella.

40
00:02:31,430 --> 00:02:33,190
Fangfang, this is my son Xiao Han.

41
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:35,910
- Hello, Auntie.
- Hello, you're so tall.

42
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,310
By the way,

43
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:39,400
Han can fetch
some umbrellas for you.

44
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,470
Yes, I'll go...

45
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,490
- Oh, no need.
- No need.

46
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:42,310
No need.

47
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,310
It's about to stop.

48
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,680
Yes, we can leave soon.

49
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,710
Alright, I'm running out of time.

50
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,580
I'll head to Mr. Zhu's place.

51
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,520
The road is slippery.

52
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,840
- Goodbye then.
- Bye.

53
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:53,280
- Goodbye.
- Watch your step. Be careful.

54
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:56,800
Let's go.

55
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,000
Let me take this.

56
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,030
Xiu'e, have a seat.

57
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,120
Make some space.

58
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,680
- What?
- Make some space.

59
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,310
Now you want to sit?

60
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,680
You said you didn't want to.

61
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,750
You occupied the seat.

62
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,080
Ridiculous.

63
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:16,400
These snacks are for my baby.

64
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:17,910
You can have some first.

65
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,520
Now you're taking them out.

66
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,000
What? You didn't ask.

67
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,630
Help me open it, okay?

68
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,000
Stop talking, just eat.

69
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,520
It's really tasty.

70
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,000
You can't open it yourself?

71
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,280
Just give me a hand.

72
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,310
Stop complaining, okay?

73
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,680
You should stop talking.

74
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,690
- Just zip it, okay?
- Try Figs.

75
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,470
Try it.

76
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,910
Did you notice one thing?

77
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,960
A good guy

78
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,960
is either someone else's son...

79
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,800
Exactly.

80
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,120
Or someone else's husband.

81
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,190
Or someone else's father.

82
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,630
Someone else's father.

83
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,400
Fangfang,

84
00:03:50,890 --> 00:03:52,490
is your daughter
at No. 2 Middle School?

85
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:53,870
- Yes.
- Which class?

86
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,030
Class 5.

87
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,800
She's Jiayue's classmate?

88
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,640
Qian Jiayue?

89
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,590
The one with big eyes.

90
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:00,710
She looks like me a lot.

91
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:01,710
She's a pretty girl.

92
00:04:01,710 --> 00:04:03,800
I've heard about Qian Jiayue.

93
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,310
Chen Mo talked about her.

94
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:06,740
- She said...
- Don't believe her.

95
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,590
Jiayue is not like her at all.

96
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:09,560
Jiayue is prettier.

97
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,520
- Not like me?
- No.

98
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,000
Ka Men doesn't take after you either.

99
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,120
It's Qing.

100
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,000
What's with Ka Men, okay?

101
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,870
Qing looks exactly the same as me!

102
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,000
Exactly the same?

103
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,890
(Welcome, Come Next Time)
Younger version of me.

104
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,720
Ice pops are here.

105
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,160
Ka Men, come on.

106
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,120
- Qian Jiayue.
- Thanks.

107
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:32,160
Chen Mo, your place is amazing.

108
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,240
I know, right?

109
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,190
Look at the CDs on the wall.

110
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,510
I was stunned when I first came.

111
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,880
Chen Mo.

112
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,870
Can I borrow these two?

113
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,190
Sure, no problem.

114
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:49,390
- Chen Mo, you have OICQ?
- Thanks.

115
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,230
I have it too.

116
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,830
Tell me your account. I'll add you.

117
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,390
Alright, no problem.

118
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,000
I want to add you too.

119
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:57,870
(Yingmo Community)

120
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,070
We've made up.

121
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,750
It was just a misunderstanding.

122
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:04,160
She's actually a very nice person.

123
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:10,360
(From Sailor)
As the poem goes,

124
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,800
