or the shortcut?

141
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,600
Main road. We have time.

142
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,920
Alright, let's go.

143
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,680
Just wait a minute.

144
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,760
