148
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,880
Good morning, Jiayue.

149
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:08,790
Morning.

150
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,400
Brother Xiao Han.

151
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:14,560
I've learned to ride a bike.

152
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,000
Let's go together today.

153
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,480
I'll host the flag-raising ceremony,

154
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,390
