155
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,480
Sorry, I can't join you.

156
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,870
I can ride really fast.

157
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,360
Don't force him, okay?

158
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,750
He's from the key class.

159
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,070
He doesn't want to play with

160
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,310
students from regular classes.

161
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,680
We shouldn't bother him.

162
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,760
Qian Jiayue.

163
00:06:31,770 --> 00:06:32,800
I really admire you.

164
00:06:33,210 --> 00:06:35,070
You can actually listen to
such a boring speech

165
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,070
and take it seriously.

166
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:38,560
She's the bigger version of Pei Dongni.

167
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,630
Talking about revising properly,

168
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,560
preparing well,

169
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,500
and summarizing mistakes.

170
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:43,920
Like we're kindergarten kids.

171
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,000
Let's welcome Xiao Han
from Class 1, Grade 10

172
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,070
to give a speech.

173
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,620
- What's wrong?
- Teacher,

174
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,000
I feel sick. I need to go home.

175
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:51,270
Is it serious? I can...

176
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,640
No need. I'll take her.

177
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,480
Alright.

178
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,320
Jiayue.

179
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:58,310
As the saying goes,
one takes the behavior

180
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,360
of one's company.

181
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,800
You should know good people.

182
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:03,480
High school years are very important.

183
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,630
- Well...
- I'm in a hurry. Bye.

184
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,110
Take care.

185
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,200
Hey...

186
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,120
Loner Xiao.

187
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,600
Take the shortcut.

188
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:16,910
We'll pass him.

189
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,440
Let's go.

190
00:07:24,220 --> 00:07:26,300
(Shanghai Puyang No. 2 Middle School)

191
00:07:26,310 --> 00:07:27,150
Class dismissed.

192
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:30,390
Goodbye, teacher.

193
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,480
Ka Men, Ka Men.

194
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,270
How was your quiz?

195
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,350
Not much done.

196
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,800
I wrote everything I knew.

197
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,720
Same here.

198
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,760
Xiao Han.

199
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,040
I'll talk to Brother Xiao Han.

200
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:48,600
What's their relationship?

201
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,230
Just neighbors.

202
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,600
Just ordinary neighbors?

203
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,270
Not that ordinary, though.

204
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,560
They grew up together.

205
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,510
Xiao Han often eats at her place.

206
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,560
Why doesn't he eat at home?

207
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,070
His dad passed early

208
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,750
when putting out a fire.

209
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,390
His mom has two jobs

210
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,480
and doesn't have time.

211
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:25,670
I see.

212
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,480
Maybe I shouldn't bother him.

213
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,080
Don't be fooled by his appearance.

214
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,920
He looks serious

215
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,480
and unapproachable,

216
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,200
but he's actually quite nice.

217
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,510
You'll find out.

218
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:46,100
(Jiale Wontons)

219
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:48,030
The green peppers are great, right?

220
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,270
Pei.

221
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,510
The business is good.

222
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,440
Is there a notice?

223
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,150
Xiu'e, look at the notice.

224
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:54,990
Three buns.

225
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:57,920
Liu Dagui.

226
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,340
- What's posted?
- Here you are.

227
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,480
What does it say?

228
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:06,480
Model Family Competition
for the 50th National Day.

229
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,910
Grand prize, Singapore-Malaysia-Thailand
tour for the whole family.

230
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:13,080
Really?
Singapore-Malaysia-Thailand tour?

231
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,920
Look.

232
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:17,480
Participate in the talent competition
with your family.

233
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,120
Talent competition, you know?

234
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:21,080
Singing, reciting, and dancing.

235
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,080
All kinds of talents.

236
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,390
Liu Songming.

237
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,840
Stop twerking.

238
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,390
You have a business.

239
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,360
Go make wontons.

240
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,100
- Tacky.
- Did you pay?

241
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,720
I shouldn't cast pearls
before swine, you know?

242
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,720
Hurry up!

243
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:35,770
Two yuan worth of buns.

244
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:38,420
(Event Details)

245
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:39,690
(Location, Time)
See you next time.

246
00:09:39,690 --> 00:09:42,580
(Win a Family Travel Prize)

247
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,200
Aiping.

248
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,240
Money's on the table.

249
00:09:48,250 --> 00:09:49,140
- I'm leaving.
- Okay.

250
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:49,990
- Thanks.
- Goodbye.

251
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:53,120
- Mr. Zhang.
- You finished?

252
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,200
Take care.

253
00:09:56,290 --> 00:09:57,200
Mr. Zhang, you're here.

254
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,630
You look handsome.

255
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,600
Tell me what you want to eat.

256
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,560
Okay, no problem.

257
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,560
Aiping.

258
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:09,750
Aiping.

259
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,200
Why are you here?

260
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,280
Don't be angry.

261
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:13,750
I shouldn't have beaten Mao Tou.

262
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,080
But I know the reason
why you're angry

263
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,200
and... and blaming me

264
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,870
is because you see me as family, right?

265
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,270
Who's your family?

266
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,560
Well...

267
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:26,870
Let's participate in
the Model Family Competition.

268
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,510
What's that got to do with us?

269
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,960
Of course it's relevant.

270
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,910
You and I are good.

271
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:34,320
Han and Mao Tou are good.

272
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,000
We're good together.

273
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,270
What nonsense are you talking about?

274
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:42,550
Actually, I want to take this chance

275
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,440
to show our relationship.

276
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:45,600
And the kids

277
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,200
can be prepared.

278
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,200
Zhang Qiming, Mr. Zhang.

279
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,510
You're here again.

280
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,790
What does it mean by again?

281
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,000
What do you want to eat?

282
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,440
Pork chop noodles.

